data.description: Welcome to 47 E. San Clemente Dr! This 4-bed 2-bath home nestled on its 5,001 sq ft lot offers established and comfortable living. Built in 2003, this property is ideal, whether you are looking for a good investment opportunity, or if you are looking for a sanctuary for you and your family.  The living area is designed for relaxation and entertainment, featuring large windows that allow for plenty of natural lighting. Adjacent to the living space, you'll find a formal dining area, perfect for hosting guests and extended family  The primary bedroom facilitates its own private full bathroom.  Three additional bedrooms ensure plenty of space for family members or guests, making this home equally practical and versatile, all while awaiting one’s personal touch.  Step outside into the backyard, where you'll find a low maintenance yard, perfect for entertaining guests.   Located in a desirable established neighborhood, this home is conveniently close to schools, parks, shopping centers, and recreational opportunities. Commuting to work or exploring nearby attractions is a breeze with easy access to major highways and public transportation.  The home is equipped with an efficient water filtration system, as well as solar panels to assist with energy consumption on those hot summer days!  Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional residence your new home. Schedule a viewing today and witness the beauty and comfort this property has to offer.
